  "_comment_gs1us_mapping": [
    "Shipping CTE per GS1 US 'EPCIS Recommendations for FSMA 204 CTEs' R2.0, §6",
    "('Aggregation Add + Object Observe' variant — pages 32-34).",
    "",
    "Event 1: TransformationEvent (creating_class_instance) — TLC-source reference for the food being shipped.",
    "Event 2: AggregationEvent (action=ADD, bizStep=packing) — pallet build. parentID = SSCC Digital Link;",
    "         childQuantityList enumerates the TLCs packed onto the pallet.",
    "Event 3: ObjectEvent (action=OBSERVE, bizStep=shipping, disposition=in_transit):",
    "         epcList = [pallet SSCC]. bizTransactionList carries desadv + bol KDEs.",
    "         sourceList/destinationList carry the shipped-from and immediate-subsequent-recipient GLNs.",
    "Shipping KDEs not shown here (ref doc type/number, date shipped) ride in the ObjectEvent's",
    "bizTransactionList + eventTime per GS1 US §6."
  ],
